@startuml
state "Waiting for New Sale" as WaitingSale
state AddingItems
state Payment
state "Sale Completed" as SaleComplete

[*] --> WaitingSale
WaitingSale --> AddingItems : New Sale
AddingItems --> Payment : All items added
Payment --> SaleComplete : Cash payment
Payment --> VerifyingPayment : Card or Check
VerifyingPayment --> SaleComplete : Payment approved
SaleComplete --> WaitingSale : Next customer

note right of VerifyingPayment
The system verifies the payment method,
checks approval status, and proceeds accordingly.
@enduml
